> 3 January - First pipeline of Turkey between Batman and Iskenderun
> 29 May - Besiktas won the championship of Turkish football league.
> 5 June - Turkish Senate 1/3 by elections
> 28 June - 504 Turks in Erenkoy enclave, Cyprus, sieged by Greek forces were evacuated.
> 8 July - President Cevdet Sunay pardons former president Celal Bayar.
> 17 September - Unity Party was founded
> 8 December - 65 soldiers in Dumlu died because of an accident.